


<div class="ref_top_section">

	<div class="landscape_photo">

		<div class="ref_wba_logo">
    <%= image_tag ("WBA.PNG") %>
		</div>

	</div>

</div>

<div class="ref_bottom_section">
	<div class="bottom_left">

		<div class="wba_acronymn box">
			 Whistle Blower's Association
		</div>

			<div class="wba_info">
			<p> Welcome to the official website for the "Whistle Blower's Association", a page dedicated to holding every official accountable
				for the calls that he makes! Here you can find the whistle rating for the officials you love to hate! You can search for your
				team's most recent game, rate the official on his or her performance, and them a comment to tell them how you feel about their calls!<br>Offical's effenciency is based on an average of the questions answered! Our current rankings table shows the officials which are believed to have
				the lowest effenciency percentage the top of the list! Where is your favorite offical on this year's current rankings? </p>

		</div>


	</div>

<div class="bottom_middle">

	<div class="bm_head">
		<div class="current_year box">
		 	2018 Rankings
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="refs_ranking_table">
		<ol>
		<% @referees_sorted_short.each do |referee| %>
				<li class="worst-ref-list">
				<%= link_to "#{referee.name}", referee_reviews_path(referee) %>
				<%= (referee.score*100).round(0) %>%
			</li>
			<% end %>
		</ol>
	</div>

	<div class="bm_middle_foot">
			<div class="rate_game_button box">
				<%= link_to "Rate Your Game's Officials", games_path %>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>

	<div class="bottom_right">
		<div class="rankings_2019_button box">
			2019 Rankings TBD
			</div><div class="rankings_2020_button box">
				2020 Rankings TBD
			</div><div class="officials_roster box">
				NBA Officials Roster
			</div><div class="officials_videos box">
				NBA Officiating Videos
			</div>

		</div>

</div>


